org.antfarmer.ejce.hibernate

Class AbstractHibernateType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antfarmer.ejce.hibernate.AbstractHibernateType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterizedType, UserType
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractLobType, EncryptedBooleanType, EncryptedByteType, EncryptedCalendarType, EncryptedCharacterType, EncryptedDateType, EncryptedDoubleType, EncryptedFloatType, EncryptedIntegerType, EncryptedLongType, EncryptedObjectType, EncryptedShortType, EncryptedStringType

    public abstract class AbstractHibernateType
extends Object
implements UserType, ParameterizedType
    Abstract Hibernate UserType class which encrypts and decrypts values transparently. This ensures data is stored in it's encrypted form in persistent storage, while not affecting it's real value in the application.
